    "lyrics": {
      "text": "Let us wor-ship the Word, O ye faith-ful, prais-ing Him that with the Fa-ther and Spir-it is co-be-gin--ning-less God, Who was born of a pure Vir-gin that we all be saved; for He was pleased to mount the Cross in the flesh that He as-sumed, ac-cept-ing thus to en-dure death. And by His glo-ri-ous__ ris--ing, He al-so willed to res-ur-rect the__ dead."
